<title>JESUH CU KA ZEIZONG A SI CH100</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawi Jesuh cu keimah ca ah, Nunnak lawmhnak a si, Nifate in ka
 thawnnak le Ka thazang a si fawn, Ngaihchiat tikah a sin ka kal, Amah
 lawng nih a ka lawmhter, Ngaihchiat tikah ka Hawi tha bik, Jesuh si.

[V2]
 Bawi Jesuh cu keimah ca ah, Hawikom thabik si, Thluachuahnak kha ka
 hal tikah, A ka pek zungzal ko, Ni a tlanter, ruah a surter, Rawl le
 lawmhnak kha a ka pek, Ni le ruah le rawl tha vialte, A ka pek.

[V3]
 Bawi Jesuh cu keimah ca ah, Zeizong vialte a si, Hi tluk zumhawk
 Hawikom tha hi, Zeitin ka hlawt khawh hnga, Amah zulh cu lam ding a si,
 Chun he zan he a ka zohkhenh, Chun he zan he ka zulh ko lai, Bawipa cu.

[V4]
 Jesuh nakin keimah caah, Hawitha deuh an um lo, Nunnak dongh tiangin
 ka zumh lai, Atu ka zumh bangin, Cu bantuk Hawi tha he nun cu, Dongh ngei
 lo nunnak nuam a si, Zungzal nunnak, zungzal lawmhnak, Keimah ca.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>